{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":0,"text":"Let me begin with four words"},{"time":3000,"text":"that will provide the context for this week,"},{"time":5000,"text":"four words that will come to define"},{"time":7000,"text":"this century."},{"time":9000,"text":"Here they are:"},{"time":11000,"text":"The Earth is full."},{"time":14000,"text":"It's full of us, it's full of our stuff,"},{"time":17000,"text":"full of our waste, full of our demands."},{"time":20000,"text":"Yes, we are a brilliant and creative species,"},{"time":23000,"text":"but we've created a little too much stuff --"},{"time":27000,"text":"so much that our economy is now bigger"},{"time":30000,"text":"than its host, our planet."}]},{"cues":[{"time":33000,"text":"This is not a philosophical statement,"},{"time":35000,"text":"this is just science"},{"time":37000,"text":"based in physics,"},{"time":39000,"text":"chemistry and biology."},{"time":42000,"text":"There are many science-based analyses of this,"},{"time":44000,"text":"but they all draw the same conclusion --"},{"time":47000,"text":"that we're living beyond our means."},{"time":50000,"text":"The eminent scientists of the Global Footprint Network, for example,"},{"time":53000,"text":"calculate that we need about 1.5 Earths"},{"time":56000,"text":"to sustain this economy."},{"time":59000,"text":"In other words,"},{"time":61000,"text":"to keep operating at our current level,"},{"time":63000,"text":"we need 50 percent more Earth than we've got."},{"time":68000,"text":"In financial terms,"},{"time":70000,"text":"this would be like always spending 50 percent more than you earn,"},{"time":74000,"text":"going further into debt every year."},{"time":76000,"text":"But of course, you can't borrow natural resources,"},{"time":79000,"text":"so we're burning through our capital,"},{"time":82000,"text":"or stealing from the future."}]},{"cues":[{"time":85000,"text":"So when I say full, I mean really full --"},{"time":88000,"text":"well past any margin for error,"},{"time":90000,"text":"well past any dispute"},{"time":92000,"text":"about methodology."},{"time":96000,"text":"What this means is our economy is unsustainable."},{"time":99000,"text":"I'm not saying it's not nice or pleasant"},{"time":102000,"text":"or that it's bad for polar bears or forests,"},{"time":104000,"text":"though it certainly is."},{"time":106000,"text":"What I'm saying"},{"time":108000,"text":"is our approach is simply unsustainable."},{"time":110000,"text":"In other words, thanks to those pesky laws of physics,"},{"time":113000,"text":"when things aren't sustainable, they stop."},{"time":116000,"text":"But that's not possible, you might think."},{"time":118000,"text":"We can't stop economic growth."},{"time":120000,"text":"Because that's what will stop: economic growth."},{"time":123000,"text":"It will stop because of the end of trade resources."},{"time":126000,"text":"It will stop because of the growing demand of us"},{"time":131000,"text":"on all the resources, all the capacity,"},{"time":133000,"text":"all the systems of the Earth,"},{"time":135000,"text":"which is now having economic damage."}]},{"cues":[{"time":140000,"text":"When we think about economic growth stopping,"},{"time":142000,"text":"we go, \"That's not possible,\""},{"time":145000,"text":"because economic growth is so essential to our society"},{"time":148000,"text":"that is is rarely questioned."},{"time":151000,"text":"Although growth has certainly delivered many benefits,"},{"time":154000,"text":"it is an idea so essential"},{"time":156000,"text":"that we tend not to understand"},{"time":158000,"text":"the possibility of it not being around."},{"time":160000,"text":"Even though it has delivered many benefits,"},{"time":162000,"text":"it is based on a crazy idea --"},{"time":165000,"text":"the crazy idea being"},{"time":167000,"text":"that we can have infinite growth"},{"time":169000,"text":"on a finite planet."},{"time":171000,"text":"And I'm here to tell you the emperor has no clothes."},{"time":174000,"text":"That the crazy idea is just that,"},{"time":176000,"text":"it is crazy,"},{"time":178000,"text":"and with the Earth full, it's game over."}]},{"cues":[{"time":180000,"text":"Come on, you're thinking."},{"time":182000,"text":"That's not possible."},{"time":184000,"text":"Technology is amazing. People are innovative."},{"time":187000,"text":"There are so many ways we can improve the way we do things."},{"time":189000,"text":"We can surely sort this out."},{"time":191000,"text":"That's all true."},{"time":193000,"text":"Well, it's mostly true."},{"time":195000,"text":"We are certainly amazing,"},{"time":197000,"text":"and we regularly solve complex problems"},{"time":199000,"text":"with amazing creativity."},{"time":201000,"text":"So if our problem"},{"time":203000,"text":"was to get the human economy down"},{"time":205000,"text":"from 150 percent to 100 percent of the Earth's capacity,"},{"time":208000,"text":"we could do that."},{"time":210000,"text":"The problem is we're just warming up"},{"time":212000,"text":"this growth engine."},{"time":214000,"text":"We plan to take this highly-stressed economy"},{"time":217000,"text":"and make it twice as big"},{"time":220000,"text":"and then make it four times as big --"},{"time":222000,"text":"not in some distant future,"},{"time":225000,"text":"but in less than 40 years,"},{"time":227000,"text":"in the life time of most of you."},{"time":230000,"text":"China plans to be there in just 20 years."},{"time":234000,"text":"The only problem with this plan"},{"time":237000,"text":"is that it's not possible."}]},{"cues":[{"time":241000,"text":"In response, some people argue,"},{"time":243000,"text":"but we need growth, we need it to solve poverty."},{"time":245000,"text":"We need it to develop technology."},{"time":247000,"text":"We need it to keep social stability."},{"time":249000,"text":"I find this argument fascinating,"},{"time":251000,"text":"as though we can kind of bend the rules of physics"},{"time":254000,"text":"to suit our needs."},{"time":259000,"text":"It's like the Earth doesn't care what we need."},{"time":262000,"text":"Mother nature doesn't negotiate;"},{"time":264000,"text":"she just sets rules and describes consequences."},{"time":267000,"text":"And these are not esoteric limits."},{"time":269000,"text":"This is about food and water, soil and climate,"},{"time":271000,"text":"the basic practical and economic foundations"},{"time":274000,"text":"of our lives."}]},{"cues":[{"time":278000,"text":"So the idea that we can smoothly transition"},{"time":281000,"text":"to a highly-efficient,"},{"time":283000,"text":"solar-powered, knowledge-based economy"},{"time":285000,"text":"transformed by science and technology"},{"time":287000,"text":"so that nine billion people"},{"time":289000,"text":"can live in 2050"},{"time":292000,"text":"a life of abundance and digital downloads"},{"time":294000,"text":"is a delusion."},{"time":297000,"text":"It's not that it's not possible to feed, clothe and house us all"},{"time":300000,"text":"and have us live decent lives."},{"time":303000,"text":"It certainly is."},{"time":305000,"text":"But the idea that we can gently grow there"},{"time":307000,"text":"with a few minor hiccups"},{"time":309000,"text":"is just wrong,"},{"time":311000,"text":"and it's dangerously wrong,"},{"time":313000,"text":"because it means we're not getting ready"},{"time":315000,"text":"for what's really going to happen."}]},{"cues":[{"time":317000,"text":"See what happens when you operate a system"},{"time":320000,"text":"past its limits"},{"time":322000,"text":"and then keep on going"},{"time":324000,"text":"at an ever-accelerating rate"},{"time":327000,"text":"is that the system stops working and breaks down."},{"time":331000,"text":"And that's what will happen to us."},{"time":338000,"text":"Many of you will be thinking,"},{"time":340000,"text":"but surely we can still stop this."},{"time":342000,"text":"If it's that bad, we'll react."},{"time":345000,"text":"Let's just think through that idea."},{"time":347000,"text":"Now we've had"},{"time":349000,"text":"50 years of warnings."},{"time":351000,"text":"We've had science proving"},{"time":354000,"text":"the urgency of change."},{"time":356000,"text":"We've had economic analysis pointing out"},{"time":358000,"text":"that, not only can we afford it,"},{"time":360000,"text":"it's cheaper to act early."},{"time":362000,"text":"And yet, the reality is"},{"time":364000,"text":"we've done pretty much nothing to change course."},{"time":367000,"text":"We're not even slowing down."},{"time":370000,"text":"Last year on climate, for example,"},{"time":372000,"text":"we had the highest global emissions ever."},{"time":374000,"text":"The story on food, on water, on soil, on climate"},{"time":377000,"text":"is all much the same."}]},{"cues":[{"time":380000,"text":"I actually don't say this in despair."},{"time":382000,"text":"I've done my grieving about the loss."},{"time":384000,"text":"I accept where we are."},{"time":386000,"text":"It is sad,"},{"time":388000,"text":"but it is what it is."},{"time":390000,"text":"But it is also time"},{"time":392000,"text":"that we ended our denial"},{"time":394000,"text":"and recognized"},{"time":396000,"text":"that we're not acting, we're not close to acting"},{"time":399000,"text":"and we're not going to act"},{"time":401000,"text":"until this crisis hits the economy."},{"time":403000,"text":"And that's why the end of growth"},{"time":405000,"text":"is the central issue"},{"time":407000,"text":"and the event that we need to get ready for."}]},{"cues":[{"time":411000,"text":"So when does this transition begin?"},{"time":413000,"text":"When does this breakdown begin?"},{"time":415000,"text":"In my view, it is well underway."},{"time":418000,"text":"I know most people don't see it that way."},{"time":420000,"text":"We tend to look at the world,"},{"time":422000,"text":"not as the integrated system that it is,"},{"time":424000,"text":"but as a series of individual issues."},{"time":426000,"text":"We see the Occupy protests,"},{"time":429000,"text":"we see spiraling debt crises,"},{"time":431000,"text":"we see growing inequality,"},{"time":433000,"text":"we see money's influence on politics,"},{"time":435000,"text":"we see resource constraint, food and oil prices."},{"time":438000,"text":"But we see, mistakenly, each of these issues"},{"time":440000,"text":"as individual problems to be solved."},{"time":444000,"text":"In fact, it's the system"},{"time":446000,"text":"in the painful process of breaking down --"},{"time":449000,"text":"our system, of debt-fueled economic growth,"},{"time":452000,"text":"of ineffective democracy,"},{"time":454000,"text":"of overloading planet Earth,"},{"time":456000,"text":"is eating itself alive."}]},{"cues":[{"time":461000,"text":"I could give you countless studies"},{"time":462000,"text":"and evidence to prove this,"},{"time":465000,"text":"but I won't because, if you want to see it,"},{"time":467000,"text":"that evidence is all around you."},{"time":470000,"text":"I want to talk to you about fear."},{"time":473000,"text":"I want to do so because, in my view,"},{"time":476000,"text":"the most important issue we face"},{"time":481000,"text":"is how we respond"},{"time":483000,"text":"to this question."},{"time":485000,"text":"The crisis is now inevitable."},{"time":488000,"text":"This issue is, how will we react?"},{"time":492000,"text":"Of course, we can't know what will happen."},{"time":495000,"text":"The future is inherently uncertain."}]},{"cues":[{"time":497000,"text":"But let's just think through what the science is telling us"},{"time":500000,"text":"is likely to happen."},{"time":503000,"text":"Imagine our economy"},{"time":506000,"text":"when the carbon bubble bursts,"},{"time":508000,"text":"when the financial markets recognize"},{"time":510000,"text":"that, to have any hope"},{"time":512000,"text":"of preventing the climate spiraling out of control,"},{"time":515000,"text":"the oil and coal industries are finished."},{"time":519000,"text":"Imagine China, India and Pakistan going to war"},{"time":522000,"text":"as climate impacts"},{"time":524000,"text":"generate conflict over food and water."},{"time":528000,"text":"Imagine the Middle East without oil income,"},{"time":531000,"text":"but with collapsing governments."},{"time":533000,"text":"Imagine our highly-tuned, just-in-time food industry"},{"time":537000,"text":"and our highly-stressed agricultural system failing"},{"time":540000,"text":"and supermarket shelves emptying."},{"time":544000,"text":"Imagine 30 percent unemployment in America"},{"time":547000,"text":"as the global economy is gripped"},{"time":549000,"text":"by fear and uncertainty."}]},{"cues":[{"time":551000,"text":"Now imagine what that means for you,"},{"time":553000,"text":"your family, your friends,"},{"time":556000,"text":"your personal financial security."},{"time":558000,"text":"Imagine what it means"},{"time":560000,"text":"for your personal security"},{"time":562000,"text":"as a heavily armed civilian population"},{"time":564000,"text":"gets angrier and angrier"},{"time":566000,"text":"about why this was allowed to happen."},{"time":570000,"text":"Imagine what you'll tell your children"},{"time":572000,"text":"when they ask you,"},{"time":574000,"text":"\"So, in 2012, Mom and Dad,"},{"time":576000,"text":"what was it like"},{"time":578000,"text":"when you'd had the hottest decade on record"},{"time":581000,"text":"for the third decade in a row,"},{"time":583000,"text":"when every scientific body in the world was saying"},{"time":586000,"text":"you've got a major problem,"},{"time":589000,"text":"when the oceans were acidifying,"},{"time":591000,"text":"when oil and food prices were spiking,"},{"time":593000,"text":"when they were rioting in the streets of London"},{"time":596000,"text":"and occupying Wall Street?"},{"time":598000,"text":"When the system was so clearly breaking down, Mom and Dad,"},{"time":601000,"text":"what did you do, what were you thinking?\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":606000,"text":"So how do you feel"},{"time":609000,"text":"when the lights go out"},{"time":611000,"text":"on the global economy in your mind,"},{"time":615000,"text":"when your assumptions about the future"},{"time":618000,"text":"fade away"},{"time":620000,"text":"and something very different emerges?"},{"time":623000,"text":"Just take a moment"},{"time":625000,"text":"and take a breath"},{"time":627000,"text":"and think, what do you feel"},{"time":630000,"text":"at this point?"},{"time":636000,"text":"Perhaps denial."},{"time":639000,"text":"Perhaps anger."},{"time":642000,"text":"Maybe fear."},{"time":647000,"text":"Of course, we can't know what's going to happen"},{"time":650000,"text":"and we have to live with uncertainty."},{"time":653000,"text":"But when we think about the kind of possibilities I paint,"},{"time":657000,"text":"we should feel a bit of fear."}]},{"cues":[{"time":661000,"text":"We are in danger, all of us,"},{"time":664000,"text":"and we've evolved to respond to danger with fear"},{"time":667000,"text":"to motivate a powerful response,"},{"time":671000,"text":"to help us bravely face a threat."},{"time":674000,"text":"But this time it's not a tiger at the cave mouth."},{"time":677000,"text":"You can't see the danger at your door."},{"time":680000,"text":"But if you look,"},{"time":682000,"text":"you can see it at the door of your civilization."},{"time":686000,"text":"That's why we need to feel our response now while the lights are still on,"},{"time":689000,"text":"because if we wait until the crisis takes hold,"},{"time":692000,"text":"we may panic and hide."},{"time":694000,"text":"If we feel it now and think it through,"},{"time":696000,"text":"we will realize we have nothing to fear"},{"time":698000,"text":"but fear itself."},{"time":703000,"text":"Yes, things will get ugly, and it will happen soon --"},{"time":706000,"text":"certainly in our lifetime --"},{"time":708000,"text":"but we are more than capable"},{"time":710000,"text":"of getting through everything that's coming."}]},{"cues":[{"time":713000,"text":"You see, those people that have faith"},{"time":716000,"text":"that humans can solve any problem,"},{"time":719000,"text":"that technology is limitless, that markets can be a force for good,"},{"time":722000,"text":"are in fact right."},{"time":724000,"text":"The only thing they're missing"},{"time":726000,"text":"is that it takes a good crisis to get us going."},{"time":729000,"text":"When we feel fear and we fear loss"},{"time":732000,"text":"we are capable of quite extraordinary things."},{"time":735000,"text":"Think about war."},{"time":738000,"text":"After the bombing of Pearl Harbor, it just took four days"},{"time":741000,"text":"for the government to ban the production of civilian cars"},{"time":743000,"text":"and to redirect the auto industry,"},{"time":745000,"text":"and from there to rationing of food and energy."},{"time":749000,"text":"Think about how a company responds to a bankruptcy threat"},{"time":752000,"text":"and how a change that seemed impossible just gets done."},{"time":755000,"text":"Think about how an individual responds"},{"time":757000,"text":"to a diagnosis of a life-threatening illness"},{"time":760000,"text":"and how lifestyle changes"},{"time":762000,"text":"that previously were just too difficult"},{"time":765000,"text":"suddenly become relatively easy."}]},{"cues":[{"time":769000,"text":"We are smart, in fact, we really are quite amazing,"},{"time":772000,"text":"but we do love a good crisis."},{"time":774000,"text":"And the good news, this one's a monster."},{"time":776000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":778000,"text":"Sure, if we get it wrong,"},{"time":780000,"text":"we could face the end of this civilization,"},{"time":782000,"text":"but if we get it right,"},{"time":784000,"text":"it could be the beginning of civilization instead."},{"time":787000,"text":"And how cool would it be"},{"time":789000,"text":"to tell your grandchildren that you were part of that?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":794000,"text":"There's certainly no technical or economic barrier in the way."},{"time":799000,"text":"Scientists like James Hansen tell us"},{"time":801000,"text":"we may need to eliminate net CO2 emissions from the economy"},{"time":804000,"text":"in just a few decades."},{"time":806000,"text":"I wanted to know what that would take,"},{"time":808000,"text":"so I worked with professor Jorgen Randers from Norway"},{"time":811000,"text":"to find the answer."},{"time":813000,"text":"We developed a plan called \"The One Degree War Plan\" --"},{"time":817000,"text":"so named because of the level of mobilization and focus required."},{"time":821000,"text":"To my surprise,"},{"time":823000,"text":"eliminating net CO2 emissions from the economy in just 20 years"},{"time":826000,"text":"is actually pretty easy and pretty cheap,"},{"time":829000,"text":"not very cheap,"},{"time":831000,"text":"but certainly less than the cost of a collapsing civilization."},{"time":834000,"text":"We didn't calculate that precisely,"},{"time":836000,"text":"but we understand that's very expensive."},{"time":839000,"text":"You can read the details,"},{"time":841000,"text":"but in summary, we can transform our economy."},{"time":843000,"text":"We can do it with proven technology."},{"time":845000,"text":"We can do it at an affordable cost."},{"time":847000,"text":"We can do it with existing political structures."},{"time":849000,"text":"The only thing we need to change"},{"time":851000,"text":"is how we think and how we feel."},{"time":854000,"text":"And this is where you come in."}]},{"cues":[{"time":857000,"text":"When we think about the future I paint,"},{"time":859000,"text":"of course we should feel a bit of fear."},{"time":861000,"text":"But fear can be paralyzing or motivating."},{"time":864000,"text":"We need to accept the fear and then we need to act."},{"time":867000,"text":"We need to act"},{"time":869000,"text":"like the future depends on it."},{"time":871000,"text":"We need to act like we only have one planet."},{"time":875000,"text":"We can do this."},{"time":877000,"text":"I know the free market fundamentalists will tell you"},{"time":880000,"text":"that more growth, more stuff and nine billion people going shopping"},{"time":883000,"text":"is the best we can do."},{"time":885000,"text":"They're wrong."},{"time":887000,"text":"We can be more,"},{"time":889000,"text":"we can be much more."},{"time":891000,"text":"We have achieved remarkable things"},{"time":894000,"text":"since working out how to grow food some 10,000 years ago."},{"time":896000,"text":"We've built a powerful foundation"},{"time":899000,"text":"of science, knowledge and technology --"},{"time":901000,"text":"more than enough to build a society"},{"time":903000,"text":"where nine billion people"},{"time":905000,"text":"can lead decent, meaningful and satisfying lives."},{"time":907000,"text":"The Earth can support that"},{"time":909000,"text":"if we choose the right path."}]},{"cues":[{"time":913000,"text":"We can choose this moment of crisis"},{"time":915000,"text":"to ask and answer the big questions of society's evolution --"},{"time":918000,"text":"like, what do we want to be when we grow up,"},{"time":921000,"text":"when we move past this bumbling adolescence"},{"time":924000,"text":"where we think there are no limits"},{"time":926000,"text":"and suffer delusions of immortality?"},{"time":929000,"text":"Well it's time to grow up,"},{"time":931000,"text":"to be wiser, to be calmer,"},{"time":933000,"text":"to be more considered."},{"time":935000,"text":"Like generations before us,"},{"time":937000,"text":"we'll be growing up in war --"},{"time":939000,"text":"not a war between civilizations,"},{"time":941000,"text":"but a war for civilization,"},{"time":943000,"text":"for the extraordinary opportunity"},{"time":945000,"text":"to build a society"},{"time":947000,"text":"which is stronger and happier"},{"time":949000,"text":"and plans on staying around"},{"time":951000,"text":"into middle age."}]},{"cues":[{"time":954000,"text":"We can choose life over fear."},{"time":956000,"text":"We can do what we need to do,"},{"time":960000,"text":"but it will take every entrepreneur,"},{"time":962000,"text":"every artist,"},{"time":964000,"text":"every scientist, every communicator,"},{"time":966000,"text":"every mother, every father, every child,"},{"time":969000,"text":"every one of us."},{"time":972000,"text":"This could be our finest hour."}]},{"cues":[{"time":975000,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":977000,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}